Published on Feb 13, 2019
Congress locks in wall solution for Trump leaves democrats in shambles! Trump wins huge. Pelosi thought she had Donald pinned down – he turned the tables on her. President Trump appeared to be moving toward approving a border security compromise after speaking with the top Republican on the Senate Appropriations Committee.
The president tweeted that he will be getting almost $23 BILLION for Border Security. The spending bill includes, $1.375 billion for physical barriers and includes a total of 55 miles, which is just 9 miles shy of Trump’s last budget request.
